{"schemaVersion":"gas-shunin-manual-law-explanation-audit/v1","reviewedAt":"2026-07-11","qualification":"gas-shunin-otsu","examYear":2021,"sourceQuestionKey":"gas-shunin:otsu:2021:law:q16","questionLabel":"問16","sourceQuestionBodyText":"消費機器の技術上の基準で規定されている次の記述のうち、誤っているものはどれか。","sourceFile":"output/gas-shunin-otsu/questions_json/2021/00_source/question_2021_1.json","explanationPatchFile":"output/gas-shunin-otsu/questions_json/2021/21_explanationText_added/question_2021_1_explanationText_added.json","sourceCorrectChoiceText":["間違い","正しい","正しい","正しい","正しい"],"patchedCorrectChoiceText":["間違い","正しい","正しい","正しい","正しい"],"correctChoiceTextMatchesSource":true,"choiceReviews":[{"choiceIndex":0,"verdict":"間違い","directBasis":["ガス事業法施行規則第202条第1項第2号イ(8)"],"basisText":"100℃超の排気筒部分は金属以外の不燃性材料で覆う。"},{"choiceIndex":1,"verdict":"正しい","directBasis":["同条第1項第4号"],"basisText":"排気筒を設ける燃焼器は所定給気開口部を持つ室に設置する。"},{"choiceIndex":2,"verdict":"正しい","directBasis":["同条第1項第1号ト"],"basisText":"12kW超の屋内ガス衣類乾燥機には排気筒を設け、所定の場合は排気フードで代替できる。"},{"choiceIndex":3,"verdict":"正しい","directBasis":["同条第1項第6号ホ"],"basisText":"密閉燃焼式ガスふろがまの給排気部先端は障害物や外気流で妨げられない位置に置く。"},{"choiceIndex":4,"verdict":"正しい","directBasis":["同条第1項第10号イ"],"basisText":"所定超高層建物の燃焼器には自動ガス遮断装置又はガス漏れ警報器を設ける。"}],"changedFields":[],"result":"reviewed_no_explanation_change_needed","sourceUrls":["https://laws.e-gov.go.jp/law/345M50000400097"]}
